    "body": "# submission name\r\n\r\noptimization_qpose_josema\r\n\r\n# archive.zip\r\n\r\nDownload:\r\n\r\n[archive.zip](https://github.com/Josemedinan/comma_video_compression_challenge/raw/submission/optimization_qpose_josema/submissions/optimization_qpose/archive.zip)\r\n\r\nIncluded in this PR:\r\n\r\n`submissions/optimization_qpose/archive.zip`\r\n\r\n# report.txt\r\n\r\n```text\r\n=== Evaluation config ===\r\n  batch_size: 16\r\n  device: mps\r\n  num_threads: 2\r\n  prefetch_queue_depth: 4\r\n  report: submissions/optimization_qpose/report.txt\r\n  seed: 1234\r\n  submission_dir: submissions/optimization_qpose\r\n  uncompressed_dir: /Users/josemedina/comma_video_compression_challenge/videos\r\n  video_names_file: /Users/josemedina/comma_video_compression_challenge/public_test_video_names.txt\r\n=== Evaluation results over 600 samples ===\r\n  Average PoseNet Distortion: 0.00061985\r\n  Average SegNet Distortion: 0.00071020\r\n  Submission file size: 277,087 bytes\r\n  Original uncompressed size: 37,545,489 bytes\r\n  Compression Rate: 0.00738003\r\n  Final score: 100*segnet_dist + √(10*posenet_dist) + 25*rate = 0.33\r\n```\r\n\r\n# does your submission require gpu for evaluation?\r\n\r\nyes\r\n\r\n# compression script included?\r\n\r\nno\r\n\r\n# notes\r\n\r\nqpose/tile-action based variant. Evaluated locally on Mac MPS.",
